Notes: CMSU holds a 40-29 lead three minutes into the second half; UMR makes a 15-1
run to take a 44-41 lead with 12:50 to go.  CMSU goes up for good on Lisa
Millham's 3-pt. basket with 11:14 to play; the 13th-ranked Jennies make 7-9 at
the line in the final 1:48 to hold off the Lady Miners.
Game.Officials: Lisa Pitts,  Ronald Miller,  Tom Sullivan
